title: Stocks Waver as Traders Stay on Sidelines Ahead of Fed, Oracle
description: US equities posted small moves on Tuesday as investors waited for clues from the Federal Reserve and artificial intelligence bellwethers about whether to go long or cash out heading into 2026.
